products with sulfites or warn them that it is present gebbie 
said as i understand it for a very sensitive person any level 
of sulfite is a problem 
the emergency rule which expires in february was approved aug 
26 by health division officials after they learned that restaurants 
were serving california table grapes and other items that treated 
with sulfites 
the rule accompanies a 1985 regulation that prohibits 
restaurants from treating fruits vegetables and other salad items 
with sulfitebased preservatives 
