on oct20 apparently to discuss tumbling oil prices at a time of 
overproduction and disarray in the world oil market opec secretary 
general subroto announced wednesday 
the announcement carried by opena the news agency of the 
13member organization of the petroleum exporting countries did 
not provide an agenda or other details 
