billion or 4316 a share up more than fivefold from earnings of 
2009 million or 784 a share a year earlier 
ninemonth revenue edged up 1 percent to 201 billion from 
199 billion a year earlier 
the ninemonth results include an 8666 million gain on the 
sale of the cbs records division to sony corp 
the new dividend up from 75 cents a share last quarter is 
payable dec 12 to shareholders of record nov 23 
